originalText.text: Jessica's team (Holanda and Olivia) got us off on the best possible foot when we moved into our new apartment. They were incredibly friendly, efficient, and needed no direction, but happily took any I provided. We really trusted Live Neatly to make suggestions for us and I was stunned by how beautiful and functional our spaces turned out. Will be having Live Neatly back for Phase 2 as we settle in further and would recommend them to anyone! Thank you, Live Neatly.

originalText.text: Jessica and her team did a five-star job organizing our new kitchen.  They listen to your requests and vision, and efficiently deliver on them.  They know the different organizer bins, separators, etc that will best optimize your space.  On top of it all, Jessica and her team are super friendly and warm.  I highly recommend them.

originalText.text: Jessica is AMAZING!  She completely organized my daughters' bedroom.  She helped them decide what to toss and what to keep.  The project was just too overwhelming to do on our own and her help was invaluable. Once they went through everything, Jessica made the room look BEAUTIFUL!  We are so happy with the way the space looks and I think they will be able to maintain it.  I can't wait to have Jessica come back and do my room next!

originalText.text: Jessica and her team have sprinkled their magic over our apartment twice. They tackled the tasks we have been meaning to do ourselves for years (and of  course never got around to) and organized our overflowing toys, kitchen and bedroom into beautiful, kid friendly spaces. They are passionate about what they do. They are kind, communicative, sensitive (so many many treasures to manage) and breathtakingly efficient. We so appreciated their attention to detail from tiny labels to keepsake organization to kid toy bins. They saved us money (no more double purchasing because we can't see what's in our pantry!), created space (storage!) and our home feels like a pleasant, calm, decluttered space to come home to now. Thank you!
